"title": "6146: deceit, and God's nature",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6146: deceit, and god's nature",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Deceit is totally contrary to the nature and purposes of God. The gospel is grounded in the complete truthfulness and trustworthiness of God, whereas sin is based upon self-deception.</p>\n<h2>God's nature and purposes are not based on deception</h2>\n<h3>Deceit is contrary to the nature of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:2\">TIT 1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:22\">1PE 2:22</a></p>\n<h3>God cannot be deceived</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:9\">1CH 28:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:1\">PSA 139:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:3\">ACT 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:5\">1CO 4:5</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ does not deceive</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:9\">ISA 53:9</a></p>\n<h3>Satan's power rests on deception</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44\">JHN 8:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:4\">GEN 3:1–3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:3\">2CO 11:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:14\">2CO 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9-2Thess2:10\">2TH 2:9–2:10</a></p>\n<h3>The coming antichrist will rely on deception</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:7\">2JN 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:24\">MAT 24:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:22\">MRK 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:14\">REV 13:14</a></p>\n<h3>False prophets and false teachers rely on deception</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:13\">2CO 11:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:14\">JER 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:26\">JER 23:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:6\">EZK 13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:30\">ACT 20:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:18\">ROM 16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:14\">EPH 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:2\">1TI 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:10-Titus1:11\">TIT 1:10–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1-2Pet2:3\">2PE 2:1–2:3</a></p>\n<h2>Deception is at the heart of human sin</h2>\n<h3>The fall took place through deception</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:4\">GEN 3:1–3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:13\">GEN 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:14\">1TI 2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Deception is a characteristic of fallen human nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:9\">JER 17:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:35\">JOB 15:35</a>PSA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:9\">5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:7\">PSA 10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:20\">PSA 35:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:3\">PSA 36:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:12\">MIC 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:13\">ROM 3:13</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:12\">PSA 38:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:11\">PSA 116:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:5\">PRO 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:4-Jer9:5\">JER 9:4–9:5</a> <em>deceptive friends and brothers</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:12\">HOS 11:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:1\">NAM 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19\">MAT 15:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21-Mark7:22\">MRK 7:21–7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:29\">ROM 1:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:13\">2TI 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:12\">TIT 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of deceit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:9\">GEN 4:9</a> <em>Cain</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:13\">GEN 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:2\">GEN 20:2</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:7\">GEN 26:7</a> <em>Isaac</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:19\">GEN 27:19</a> <em>Jacob</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:7\">GEN 31:7</a> <em>Laban</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:31\">GEN 37:31</a> <em>Joseph's brothers</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:29\">EXO 8:29</a> <em>Pharaoh</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:4\">JOS 9:4</a> <em>the Gibeonites</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:2\">1SA 21:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:13\">1SA 21:13</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:6\">2SA 13:6</a> <em>Amnon</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:18\">1KI 13:18</a> <em>the old prophet</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:22\">2KI 5:22</a> <em>Gehazi</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:8\">MAT 2:8</a> <em>Herod</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:18\">MAT 22:18</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:15\">MRK 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:23\">LUK 20:23</a></p>",
